Twitter Coverage of AusPreserves

Peter Neish

2018-02-16 04:40:10

1 Introduction

An analysis of tweets from auspreserves. Code is available on GitHub.

286 tweets were collected using the rtweet R package:

auspreserves <- search_tweets("#auspreserves", 10000)
saveRDS(auspreserves, "data/auspreserves.rds")
